org.ontouml.model.Decoratable<PropertyStereotype>
org.ontouml.model.Property
public final class Property extends Decoratable<PropertyStereotype>
A decoratable element that represents an attribute of a class, or one end of a relation. Examples include the attribute "name" of the class "Person", and the ends of the binary relation "studies in" connected to the classes "Student" and "University." Instances of class and relation elements bear values for the properties these classifiers contain, according to the constraints specified within each property. For example, the value assigned to a property in an instance must be itself an instance of the classifier in property type.
